headline: LPL Financial Holdings Inc. (LPLA) Q2 Earnings Surpass Estimates
summary: LPL Financial (LPLA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +7.13% and -0.29%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
